      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "引子",
      "speakers": [
        "虞姬"
      ],
      "text": "一身曾沐君恩宠，暖帐亲承奉。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901107_e00003",
      "play_id": "70901107",
      "scene_id": "70901107_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 3,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "虞姬"
      ],
      "text": "玉容未必倾城国，椒房宠爱君恩极。海棠睡起春正娇，莫把金珠污颜色。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901107_e00004",
      "play_id": "70901107",
      "scene_id": "70901107_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 4,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "虞姬"
      ],
      "text": "妾乃虞姬也。自配楚王，指望江山一统，岂知天不遂志，瓦解冰消。目下四处歌声骤起，楚军尽皆逃散，妾身急往叩报。怎奈大王全不运筹善策，只在帐内长叹。看看汉兵已至，眼看大势去也。",
      "text_length": 85
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901107_e00005",
      "play_id": "70901107",
      "scene_id": "70901107_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 5,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "内白",
      "speakers": [
        "项羽"
      ],
      "text": "哇呀……",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901107_e00006",
      "play_id": "70901107",
      "scene_id": "70901107_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 6,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "虞姬"
      ],
      "text": "言之未已，大王升帐来也。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901107_e00007",
      "play_id": "70901107",
      "scene_id": "70901107_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 7,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "项羽上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
