      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "众兵同摆阵，韩信领众兵同下。虞姬、项羽同上。",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901107_e00028",
      "play_id": "70901107",
      "scene_id": "70901107_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 28,
      "seq_in_scene": 28,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "泣颜回",
      "speakers": [
        "项羽"
      ],
      "text": "我腰间仗剑吐虹霓，空自有拔山之力。天亡吾楚，看看食尽兵疲。听歌声四起汉兵围，吹散了八千队。",
      "text_length": 45
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901107_e00029",
      "play_id": "70901107",
      "scene_id": "70901107_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 29,
      "seq_in_scene": 29,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "项羽"
      ],
      "text": "美人！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901107_e00030",
      "play_id": "70901107",
      "scene_id": "70901107_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 30,
      "seq_in_scene": 30,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "泣颜回",
      "speakers": [
        "项羽"
      ],
      "text": "我和你难免分离，禁不住两行珠泪。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901107_e00031",
      "play_id": "70901107",
      "scene_id": "70901107_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 31,
      "seq_in_scene": 31,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "钟离昧上。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901107_e00032",
      "play_id": "70901107",
      "scene_id": "70901107_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 32,
      "seq_in_scene": 32,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "不是路",
      "speakers": [
        "钟离昧"
      ],
      "text": "垓下重围，帐里将军知也未？",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901107_e00033",
      "play_id": "70901107",
      "scene_id": "70901107_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 33,
      "seq_in_scene": 33,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "钟离昧"
      ],
      "text": "报，大王不好了！",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901107_e00034",
      "play_id": "70901107",
      "scene_id": "70901107_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 34,
      "seq_in_scene": 34,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "项羽"
      ],
      "text": "为何的？",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901107_e00035",
      "play_id": "70901107",
      "scene_id": "70901107_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 35,
      "seq_in_scene": 35,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "钟离昧"
      ],
      "text": "大王，那韩信统兵十万众，围住垓下，事在危急了！",
      "text_length": 23
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901107_e00036",
      "play_id": "70901107",
      "scene_id": "70901107_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 36,
      "seq_in_scene": 36,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "不是路",
      "speakers": [
        "钟离昧"
      ],
      "text": "四下里，腾腾横杀气。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901107_e00037",
      "play_id": "70901107",
      "scene_id": "70901107_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 37,
      "seq_in_scene": 37,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "项羽"
      ],
      "text": "有这等事！起过了。啊呀美人吓！我英雄志，当初指望造鸿基。",
      "text_length": 28
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901107_e00038",
      "play_id": "70901107",
      "scene_id": "70901107_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 38,
      "seq_in_scene": 38,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "虞姬"
      ],
      "text": "如今呢？",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901107_e00039",
      "play_id": "70901107",
      "scene_id": "70901107_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 39,
      "seq_in_scene": 39,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "项羽"
      ],
      "text": "到如今，",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901107_e00040",
      "play_id": "70901107",
      "scene_id": "70901107_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 40,
      "seq_in_scene": 40,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "项羽"
      ],
      "text": "一旦成虚废！我项羽此行，那韩信纵有十万之众，孤家何足惧哉！只是行军之际，怎生带得你行。也罢！我闻汉王乃好色之徒，你可好生扶侍他去吧！",
      "text_length": 66
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901107_e00041",
      "play_id": "70901107",
      "scene_id": "70901107_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 41,
      "seq_in_scene": 41,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "虞姬"
      ],
      "text": "大王说哪里话来，自古忠臣不事二君，烈女不嫁二夫。大王欲图天下大事，岂可以贱妾为累，愿以此身报大王之恩也。",
      "text_length": 52
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901107_e00042",
      "play_id": "70901107",
      "scene_id": "70901107_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 42,
      "seq_in_scene": 42,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "虞姬"
      ],
      "text": "不须疑，",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901107_e00043",
      "play_id": "70901107",
      "scene_id": "70901107_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 43,
      "seq_in_scene": 43,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "虞姬"
      ],
      "text": "大王！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901107_e00044",
      "play_id": "70901107",
      "scene_id": "70901107_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 44,
      "seq_in_scene": 44,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "虞姬"
      ],
      "text": "赐我三尺青锋先刎死。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901107_e00045",
      "play_id": "70901107",
      "scene_id": "70901107_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 45,
      "seq_in_scene": 45,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "项羽"
      ],
      "text": "啊呀美人，你果有此心？",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901107_e00046",
      "play_id": "70901107",
      "scene_id": "70901107_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 46,
      "seq_in_scene": 46,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "虞姬"
      ],
      "text": "果有此心。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901107_e00047",
      "play_id": "70901107",
      "scene_id": "70901107_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 47,
      "seq_in_scene": 47,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "项羽"
      ],
      "text": "你实有此意？",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901107_e00048",
      "play_id": "70901107",
      "scene_id": "70901107_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 48,
      "seq_in_scene": 48,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "虞姬"
      ],
      "text": "实有此意。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901107_e00049",
      "play_id": "70901107",
      "scene_id": "70901107_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 49,
      "seq_in_scene": 49,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "项羽"
      ],
      "text": "罢，罢，罢！我项羽就死在九泉之下，也得瞑目矣！啊呀美人，只是孤家舍你不得！",
      "text_length": 37
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901107_e00050",
      "play_id": "70901107",
      "scene_id": "70901107_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 50,
      "seq_in_scene": 50,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "虞姬"
      ],
      "text": "大王舍了吧！",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901107_e00051",
      "play_id": "70901107",
      "scene_id": "70901107_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 51,
      "seq_in_scene": 51,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "项羽"
      ],
      "text": "舍不得！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901107_e00052",
      "play_id": "70901107",
      "scene_id": "70901107_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 52,
      "seq_in_scene": 52,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "虞姬"
      ],
      "text": "大王舍了吧！",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901107_e00053",
      "play_id": "70901107",
      "scene_id": "70901107_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 53,
      "seq_in_scene": 53,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "项羽"
      ],
      "text": "舍不得！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901107_e00054",
      "play_id": "70901107",
      "scene_id": "70901107_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 54,
      "seq_in_scene": 54,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "虞姬"
      ],
      "text": "汉兵围得紧了。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901107_e00055",
      "play_id": "70901107",
      "scene_id": "70901107_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 55,
      "seq_in_scene": 55,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "项羽"
      ],
      "text": "闪开了！哇呀……嘿！罢，罢，罢！我就把青锋付与伊。呣，老亚夫啊老亚夫！",
      "text_length": 35
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901107_e00056",
      "play_id": "70901107",
      "scene_id": "70901107_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 56,
      "seq_in_scene": 56,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "虞姬"
      ],
      "text": "大王请上，妾身有一拜。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901107_e00057",
      "play_id": "70901107",
      "scene_id": "70901107_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 57,
      "seq_in_scene": 57,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "唱",
      "speakers": [
        "虞姬"
      ],
      "text": "分别去，除非梦里重相会。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901107_e00058",
      "play_id": "70901107",
      "scene_id": "70901107_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 58,
      "seq_in_scene": 58,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "虞姬自刎，下。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901107_e00059",
      "play_id": "70901107",
      "scene_id": "70901107_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 59,
      "seq_in_scene": 59,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "钟离昧"
      ],
      "text": "大王，虞娘娘自刎了！",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901107_e00060",
      "play_id": "70901107",
      "scene_id": "70901107_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 60,
      "seq_in_scene": 60,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "项羽"
      ],
      "text": "怎、怎、怎么说？",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901107_e00061",
      "play_id": "70901107",
      "scene_id": "70901107_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 61,
      "seq_in_scene": 61,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "钟离昧"
      ],
      "text": "虞娘娘自刎了！",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901107_e00062",
      "play_id": "70901107",
      "scene_id": "70901107_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 62,
      "seq_in_scene": 62,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "项羽"
      ],
      "text": "啊！啊呀美人吓！看看粉消玉碎，粉消玉碎！",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901107_e00063",
      "play_id": "70901107",
      "scene_id": "70901107_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 63,
      "seq_in_scene": 63,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "扑灯蛾",
      "speakers": [
        "项羽"
      ],
      "text": "可怜一妇人，可怜一妇人，激烈男儿志。甘自把身躯须臾丧我龙泉也。",
      "text_length": 31
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901107_e00064",
      "play_id": "70901107",
      "scene_id": "70901107_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 64,
      "seq_in_scene": 64,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "项羽"
      ],
      "text": "啊呀美人吓！",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901107_e00065",
      "play_id": "70901107",
      "scene_id": "70901107_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 65,
      "seq_in_scene": 65,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "扑灯蛾",
      "speakers": [
        "项羽"
      ],
      "text": "魂飞魄散，好叫我一身无计。到如今，怎生区处，只恐汉兵又来至。",
      "text_length": 30
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901107_e00066",
      "play_id": "70901107",
      "scene_id": "70901107_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 66,
      "seq_in_scene": 66,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "扑灯蛾",
      "speakers": [
        "钟离昧"
      ],
      "text": "大王休迟滞，大王休迟滞。顷刻汉兵至，若还不出战，及早收兵回避也。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901107_e00067",
      "play_id": "70901107",
      "scene_id": "70901107_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 67,
      "seq_in_scene": 67,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "项羽"
      ],
      "text": "闪开了！虞姬，美人……我就把……哇呀……青锋取首级。马来！",
      "text_length": 29
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901107_e00068",
      "play_id": "70901107",
      "scene_id": "70901107_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 68,
      "seq_in_scene": 68,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "钟离昧"
      ],
      "text": "吓。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901107_e00069",
      "play_id": "70901107",
      "scene_id": "70901107_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 69,
      "seq_in_scene": 69,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "扑灯蛾",
      "speakers": [
        "项羽"
      ],
      "text": "且将来，马上悬之。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901107_e00070",
      "play_id": "70901107",
      "scene_id": "70901107_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 70,
      "seq_in_scene": 70,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "项羽"
      ],
      "text": "虞姬……美人！",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901107_e00071",
      "play_id": "70901107",
      "scene_id": "70901107_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 71,
      "seq_in_scene": 71,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "扑灯蛾",
      "speakers": [
        "项羽"
      ],
      "text": "愿生死同归一处，管叫恁，名登青史，留下好名儿。",
      "text_length": 23
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901107_e00072",
      "play_id": "70901107",
      "scene_id": "70901107_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 72,
      "seq_in_scene": 72,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "项羽"
      ],
      "text": "啊呀美人！",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70901107_e00073",
      "play_id": "70901107",
